_sText: This is another nice map by Nipper which is based in and on two pirate ships facing eachother this is similar to another map in our database but it is not destructible but, anyway the map is great for small/medium firefights between two teams kind of like a duel in a way but it depends on your thought for what you use it for but the design of the map is very well done it really re-creates the feeling of being on a pirate ship (Or not) try it out.
